WEBVTT

1
00:00:20.062 --> 00:00:23.232
[funky hip-hop beat layers in]

2
00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:33.802
[man] Previously
on Raising Kanan...

3
00:00:33.826 --> 00:00:35.536
In Chinese mythology.

4
00:00:35.703 --> 00:00:37.580
there's a monster called Hundun.

5
00:00:37.747 --> 00:00:40.332
A blind. deaf. faceless demon.

6
00:00:40.499 --> 00:00:42.376
Hundun is chaos.

7
00:00:42.501 --> 00:00:43.836
[sharp. jarring gunshots]

8
00:00:43.961 --> 00:00:46.338
-[glass shatters]
-[gunfire]

9
00:00:46.505 --> 00:00:47.298
Evil.

10
00:00:47.465 --> 00:00:49.091
Corrupting and polluting

11
00:00:49.258 --> 00:00:50.760
all that it touches.

12
00:00:50.926 --> 00:00:53.471
Raq hired some dirty police
to kill your friend.

13
00:00:53.637 --> 00:00:56.599
[Irwin] What's most scary
about Hundun's true evil...

14
00:00:56.766 --> 00:00:58.768
-We in business. Hafiz.
-Isn't what it does...

15
00:00:58.934 --> 00:01:00.811
You gon' do what they won't?

16
00:01:00.936 --> 00:01:01.936
Where is it?

17
00:01:02.688 --> 00:01:04.482
But that it can't see itself.

18
00:01:04.607 --> 00:01:07.985
Just 'cause you didn't see me

19
00:01:08.152 --> 00:01:09.820
didn't mean I didn't see you.

20
00:01:09.987 --> 00:01:12.531
[Irwin] It doesn't know
that it's a monster.

21
00:01:12.698 --> 00:01:13.991
[gunshot]

22
00:01:14.784 --> 00:01:17.119
Just like you.

23
00:01:17.286 --> 00:01:18.579
We both got family. 'Nique.

24
00:01:18.704 --> 00:01:20.664
I'm a street nigga
who do street nigga shit.

25
00:01:20.831 --> 00:01:23.375
I'm ready to go back to war
next to y'all.

26
00:01:23.542 --> 00:01:25.586
If you want work.
I got work for you.

27
00:01:25.753 --> 00:01:27.113
Both of you get
in the fuckin' car.

28
00:01:27.170 --> 00:01:28.398
Come on. baby.
It's gon' be all right.

29
00:01:28.422 --> 00:01:29.256
Let's go. nigga.

30
00:01:29.423 --> 00:01:30.966
But you need to step up

31
00:01:31.091 --> 00:01:32.384
and take care of your daughter.

32
00:01:32.551 --> 00:01:34.136
I know...
You don't think I know that?

33
00:01:34.303 --> 00:01:35.447
[Krystal] And I am worried
you're gonna do

34
00:01:35.471 --> 00:01:36.847
somethin' crazy about Famous.

35
00:01:36.972 --> 00:01:38.015
Famous was my brother.

36
00:01:38.182 --> 00:01:39.182
But he wouldn't want you

37
00:01:39.265 --> 00:01:40.643
to fuck yourself up for him.

38
00:01:40.810 --> 00:01:42.311
[Captain Baptiste]
There's no world

39
00:01:42.478 --> 00:01:44.188
where the murder of a cop
goes unanswered.

40
00:01:44.354 --> 00:01:46.315
Squeeze hard on anyone you can.

41
00:01:46.482 --> 00:01:47.691
[Garcia] I'm police.

42
00:01:47.817 --> 00:01:48.901
She's safe with me.

43
00:01:49.026 --> 00:01:50.360
They found the Jane Doe

44
00:01:50.527 --> 00:01:51.946
in a stairwell over at Edgemere.

45
00:01:52.071 --> 00:01:53.632
One of the tenants had said
that they saw

46
00:01:53.656 --> 00:01:55.016
a Black woman leaving
the apartment

47
00:01:55.115 --> 00:01:56.509
where we think your friend
was murdered.

48
00:01:56.533 --> 00:01:58.202
-[gunshot]
-Call the police.

49
00:01:58.327 --> 00:02:00.222
tell 'em some white boy
with tattoos came in here

50
00:02:00.246 --> 00:02:01.515
and did all of that
to these people.

51
00:02:01.539 --> 00:02:03.457
[tense music playing]

52
00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:08.294
Phil Russo and his fuckin' gang
of misfits in Jersey

53
00:02:08.461 --> 00:02:10.172
think they can go toe-to-toe
with me now.

54
00:02:10.297 --> 00:02:12.466
I overstepped. and I apologize.

55
00:02:13.175 --> 00:02:15.135
[grunting]

56
00:02:15.261 --> 00:02:17.429
We look out for ours
on this side.

57
00:02:17.596 --> 00:02:19.682
You got the streets wired
with these bike niggas.

58
00:02:19.849 --> 00:02:21.350
You and me join forces?

59
00:02:21.475 --> 00:02:22.619
[Snaps] We want a bigger piece
of the pie

60
00:02:22.643 --> 00:02:23.853
out on Southside. Jamaica.

61
00:02:24.019 --> 00:02:25.396
And we got our own supplier.

62
00:02:25.563 --> 00:02:27.147
[Snaps] We bring together
you and Unique

63
00:02:27.314 --> 00:02:28.750
and then connect you
with our nephew.

64
00:02:28.774 --> 00:02:30.192
Niggas call me Breeze.

65
00:02:30.359 --> 00:02:31.359
Word.

66
00:02:32.111 --> 00:02:34.196
You don't know that
it was Raq. Kanan.

67
00:02:34.363 --> 00:02:35.990
If you ain't with me.
you against me.

68
00:02:36.156 --> 00:02:37.783
[ominous music playing]

69
00:02:37.950 --> 00:02:39.034
Why'd you kill Krystal?

70
00:02:39.201 --> 00:02:40.828
I didn't kill your girlfriend.

71
00:02:40.953 --> 00:02:42.371
I know you killed Fame too.

72
00:02:42.538 --> 00:02:45.040
I'm done making excuses for you
and for me.

73
00:02:45.207 --> 00:02:47.126
Tonight. I'ma do what
I shoulda done.

74
00:02:47.293 --> 00:02:49.670
I would never hurt you
like that. I love you.

75
00:02:49.837 --> 00:02:52.006
Only person you ever loved
is you.

76
00:02:52.172 --> 00:02:54.925
[music intensifies]

77
00:02:56.427 --> 00:02:58.387
♪ I'm a hustla. baby ♪

78
00:02:58.554 --> 00:03:00.097
-♪ I'm a hustla. baby ♪
-♪ Yeah ♪

79
00:03:00.264 --> 00:03:02.391
