On this side ♪

106
00:03:59.281 --> 00:04:00.908
♪ Niggas get to it
On this side ♪

107
00:04:01.075 --> 00:04:03.452
♪ I know heartbreaks
Setbacks ♪

108
00:04:03.619 --> 00:04:05.788
♪ Bitch. if I crap out
I'm sure I'ma get back ♪

109
00:04:05.955 --> 00:04:07.355
♪ I been through
The ups and downs ♪

110
00:04:07.414 --> 00:04:08.999
♪ You know I get around ♪

111
00:04:09.166 --> 00:04:10.834
♪ So to me. it's all a part
