112
00:04:11.001 --> 00:04:13.587
♪ If I ain't the coke man
Or the dope man ♪

113
00:04:13.754 --> 00:04:15.923
♪ I'm almost for sure. man
I gotta take it ♪

114
00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:18.300
♪ No need to say shit
I'm gon' take it ♪

115
00:04:18.466 --> 00:04:21.136
♪ Robberies turn homicide
It's nothin' to play with ♪

116
00:04:21.303 --> 00:04:22.303
