here tonight.

178
00:09:04.378 --> 00:09:05.462
Not ever.

179
00:09:07.547 --> 00:09:09.591
And I'm not just talkin'
about police.

180
00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:11.385
That shit go without sayin'.

181
00:09:13.887 --> 00:09:16.007
Talkin' about your nearest
and fuckin' dearest. nigga.

182
00:09:17.516 --> 00:09:18.600
Can't tell nobody.

183
00:09:20.143 --> 00:09:21.895
That shit gotta go to the grave
with you.

184
00:09:24.189 --> 00:09:25.565
I'm sorry about it.

185
00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:39.621
[window whirring]

186
00:09:40.414 --> 00:09:41.748
Yo. Ruben.

187
00:09:43.250 --> 00:09:45.090
Let me hit you off
for this extra work tonight.

188
00:09:46.378 --> 00:09:47.587
I'm good.

189
00:09:48.255 --> 00:09:49.256
Nah.

190
00:09:49.923 --> 00:09:51.550
Nah. this shit
was above and beyond.

191
00:09:53.051 --> 00:09:54.136
[sighs]

192
00:10:00.642 --> 00:10:01.727
-[gunshots]
-[Ruben grunts]

193
00:10:01.893 --> 00:10:05.355
[intense dramatic music playing]

194
00:10:09.234 --> 00:10:11.320
[dog barking in distance]

195
00:10:20.329 --> 00:10:24.833
[siren wailing]

196
00:10:24.958 --> 00:10:28.211
[ominous music playing]

197
00:10:31.256 --> 00:10:33.050
