212
00:12:14.151 --> 00:12:15.777
Was going over there real angry.

213
00:12:16.862 --> 00:12:18.572
I got worried.

214
00:12:18.738 --> 00:12:20.198
Reached Uncle Lou.

215
00:12:20.365 --> 00:12:22.365
