and check on shit.

216
00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:25.537
I ain't heard nothin'
about any of that.

217
00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:28.957
Been callin' Kanan
and Uncle Lou. but...

218
00:12:29.624 --> 00:12:30.959
