That's you.

221
00:12:41.470 --> 00:12:42.721
[door opens]

222
00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.723
[door closes]

223
00:12:47.225 --> 00:12:48.225
Police.

224
00:12:51.313 --> 00:12:53.023
Marvin Thomas?

225
00:12:55.734 --> 00:12:57.110
Is Louis Thomas your brother?

226
00:13:00.989 --> 00:13:02.949
[muffled chatter in distance]

227
00:13:03.116 --> 00:13:04.868
♪ I told you ♪

228
00:13:05.911 --> 00:13:08.371
♪ That I would never
Betray you ♪

229
00:13:08.538 --> 00:13:11.124
♪ But you ♪

230
00:13:11.249 --> 00:13:15.337
♪ You took my trust
And left me in the dust ♪

231
